# Logs
logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
lerna-debug.log*

node_modules
dist
dist-ssr
dev-dist
coverage
*.local

# Env — never commit secrets. .env.example is the documented template.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Net Worth — real private balances must never be committed. The sanitized
# templates/networth-seed-template.csv is the only Net Worth CSV that should be tracked.
*-filled.csv
*.local.csv
networth-*.csv
!templates/networth-seed-template.csv

